    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Actually, we have another open issue with regard to the CSS classes of the refinement list and the number of active elements. The fact that we might need it on other widgets does not change anything about the fact that it is needed here.\n\nI don't want to add a `.has-only-one-page` class, it's too specific. I'll stick with the `pagecount`, but using the current number of displayed pages instead.\n",
