  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I really don't think we need that today, the small snippet I put solves this without us having to add more API. The need to \"hide\" the pagination here is only valid for our use case. As a user I prefer to know when there's only one page, while if you hide it I will just think \"Maybe there are more pages, but I cannot tell\"\n",
