  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Having to create a whole new widget (even a simple one) seems way more complex than simply styling a CSS class. I don't see adding this new CSS as a new API for instantsearch, it in the same vein as all the other `__active` classes we are adding to all our components. Just denoting the current state through CSS classes so users can style their widgets accordingly.\n",
